Create pymongo Layer

mkdir python
pip install pymongo -t python/
zip -r pymongo-layer.zip python

Upload the Layer

----------------

add environment variables:

DB_NAME = photos
MONGO_HOST = 10.0.1.110
MONGO_PASS = password
MONGO_PORT = 27017
MONGO_USER = root

-----------------

Timeout - 2 min

-----------------

Add trigger.
go to s3 -> Properties -> Event notifications

-----------------

